 smaller \"B\" particles which make it a good\nglass former. Although the glass forming binary systems studied here are quite\nsimilar, differing only in composition, we find that their glass forming\nability cannot be attributed to a single phenomena.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2016 10:35:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-03"}
