ations directly depend on chromospheric\nactivity. Comparing the system with its analogue it is seen that the activity\nlevel of KIC 9641031 is remarkablely lower than the others.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2016 10:45:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-04"}
