al\napproaches match the simulation results, and the proposed equalization\nalgorithms can significantly improve the BER performance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2016 13:07:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Jun 2018 19:23:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-07"}
