 show that the proposed\nformulation can track hundreds of targets efficiently and improves state-of-art\nresults by significant margins on eleven challenging high density crowd\nsequences.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2016 15:11:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-29"}
